Class OCommandScript

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.orientechnologies.orient.core.command.OCommandRequestAbstract

  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    public class OCommandScript
extends OCommandRequestTextAbstract
    Script command request implementation. It just stores the request and delegated the execution to the configured OCommandExecutor.
    Author:
    Luca Garulli (l.garulli--(at)--orientdb.com)
    See Also:
    OCommandExecutorScript
